  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4246538/" class="title-link">大哉易子</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4246538"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lsyzl/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3095964-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lsyzl/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">牵手到老</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-10-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-10-30 15:10:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4246538_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如果两千年后人类文明还存在的话，哪些发源于当代的思想还会存在？这是个无法回答的问题。但是相对于我们当代文明来说，诞生于两千多年的诸子百家思想却一直影响着我们。  本书中，易先生从诸子中选出对大众最有影响力的儒，道，墨，法四大家，不但分别介绍了他们的特点与领军...

